<title>AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Packer said buying SHC management contract.</title>
<headline>RTRS-Packer said buying SHC management contract.</headline>
<dateline>SYDNEY 1996-01-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Australia's best known gambler, Kerry Packer, is expected to make a bid to buy a controlling interest in the management contract of the Sydney Harbour Casino, Australian newspapers reported on Monday.</p>
<p>&quot;Mr Packer's listed Publishing and Broadcasting (Ltd) company will spend A$240 million to buy 85 percent of the Sydney Harbour Casino's lucrative management contract from the American Showboat (Inc) casino and hotel group,&quot; The Daily Telegraph reported on Monday.</p>
<p>Showboat also holds a 26.1 percent stake in Sydney Harbour Casino Holdings Ltd, which owns the Sydney casino.</p>
